text: Who’s everyone picking tonight? I‘ll be rooting for #TeamLeBron! #AllStarGame
I hope Congress can protect the #DACA population AND provide for needed border security. The American people want results. Rs & Ds should work together to make this happen.
Hope everyone is enjoying the #WinterOlympics. Favorite moment so far? Mine is seeing the #Ohio kid Red Gerard win gold.
Good luck to one of the newest members of the @cavs family, @Larrydn22, in the #SlamDunkContest tonight! It’s been fun to watch him energize the Cavs.

Yesterday's indictment of 13 Russian nationals & three Russian entities for interfering in the 2016 presidential election was a positive step toward holding #Russia accountable. The American people deserve answers.

#Russia has been attempting to undermine our democracy for decades. And they will continue to do so. We must not lose sight of the bigger picture, & take serious steps to combat their propaganda and disinformation campaigns.

The negative impact on our economy, on #jobs & our workers of having profits locked out of the U.S. makes no sense & is why I fought to reform our international tax code. This announcement by @Cisco & others is one of many indicators that #taxreform is working as intended
Heartbreaking news out of Florida. Jane and I send our prayers to the school, the community, and the victims of this tragedy.

The Pentagon’s latest National Defense Strategy highlights the harsh realities of the threats we face in the world & the steps we need to take to confront them. We must invest in our men & women in uniform and give them the tools they need now and in the future to do their jobs.

#NorthKorea is a vicious, brutal regime that systematically abuses the natural rights of its own citizens. It survives on total repression, fear & propaganda. NK must be called out for what it is, and the West must not legitimize those who enable & benefit from this cruel regime.

The #opioidcrisis is having a devastating impact on #Ohio communities, families, local budgets, the criminal justice system & more. We must take a more aggressive role at the national level to help turn the tide.
Praying for the families of two police officers killed in the line of duty today in Westerville. A tragic reminder of the danger men and women protecting us face every day.
Inspirational message at the #NationalPrayerBreakfast from Reps @SteveScalise and @CedricRichmond on how faith can help us rise above politics.
Pleased to see there is a bipartisan budget agreement to provide additional funding to combat the #opioidcrisis & support our military. Look forward to reviewing the details of this proposal.
Pleased to welcome @realDonaldTrump to Cincinnati today for a visit to Sheffer Corporation, an #Ohio company investing in new plants and equipment & giving workers bonuses as a result of #taxreform.

With the #Olympics fast approaching, we remember Ohioan Jesse Owens. He inspired a nation, stood up to tyranny, & helped advance the cause of racial equality through not only his athletic prowess, but the content of his character. #Olympics #BlackHistoryMonth
This month, we celebrate the many contributions & achievements African-Americans have made to #Ohio & the U.S. #BlackHistoryMonth

I’m hopeful that we can make progress this year on strengthening our workforce development programs, rebuilding our aging infrastructure, & combating the #opioidcrisis that, in some cases, is undermining employers’ efforts to hire the workers they need. #Jobs

Jane and I were on the train this morning traveling to the House and Senate Republican Member retreat. We are both fine. We are keeping those who were injured in our prayers and are grateful for the first responders who quickly arrived on the scene.
As POTUS mentioned in his #SOTU speech, we are already seeing the benefits of regulatory relief & the new #taxreform law. We know that more must be done. #Jobs

Infrastructure permitting reform is important to creating #jobs. Glad to see #POTUS discussing its importance. We’re making progress on this through my 2015 bill to make permitting smarter & more efficient.

Otto Warmbier was a remarkable young man. It was very moving to see #POTUS honor his memory & recognize the Warmbier family tonight. Jane and I had another good visit with them today, and we continue to lift them up in our prayers.

The #opioidcrisis and the uptick in #humantrafficking are directly related. It will take a societal effort to help turn the tide of addiction and #endhumantrafficking, but the gov't has a role to play.
Today is International Holocaust Remembrance Day. #WeRemember the 6 million Jews who perished and renew our commitment to stand against evil and oppression wherever we find it.

Gov’t shutdowns ultimately hurt our economy, hurt families, and hurt our troops. Pleased that a sufficient number of my Democratic colleagues joined Republicans in voting to re-open the federal gov’t today. #Ohio

Today, we have a choice. We can vote to extend this critical funding for our nation’s children, or we can continue to kick the can down the road & create instability for these families in need. My choice is clear: #ExtendCHIP
Pleased to see Congress will consider a six-year #CHIP re-authorization this week. 219,000 #Ohio kids need Congress to enact a long-term funding solution to #ExtendCHIP. Congress must act. #SaveCHIP

All over the country, there are companies large & small that have announced pay increases, or bonuses, or increased 401(k) contributions, or increased pension contributions, or new investments in equipment and technology b/c of #taxreform

#HumanTrafficking has moved from the street corner, to the smart phone. Tragically, evil websites like Backpage have taken advantage of an archaic 1996 law that allows them to operate with immunity. #SESTA

When most people I talk to learn that #humantrafficking is happening all over #Ohio & this country, that young women & children are being sold online for sex in this country, they are shocked. But that is the reality and why we need #SESTA

This wk, POTUS signed into law the bipartisan INTERDICT Act to help combat the #opioidepidemic. This bill will ensure we get the needed funds for screening equipment, but more must be done. Senate must also take up #STOPAct to identify the shipments & help keep fentanyl out.

On top of these business incentives & the beneficial results we are already seeing of more investment, workers & families will also get individual tax cuts: @USTreasury says abt 90% of employees are abt to see less withholding from the paycheck & more help for the family budget.

#TaxReform is good for American workers. More #jobs, better pay & benefits, and better tools, including new technology & equipment. And for workers competing w/ foreign companies, we leveled the playing field: they no longer have to compete w/ one hand tied behind their back.
I also heard abt how the new lower tax rates and immediate expensing is responsible for increased investments in workers, more investment in plant and equipment and more #jobs. #TaxReform
At Sheffer Corporation in Cincinnati, Wolf Metals in Columbus, and Tremco in Cleveland, I had town hall meetings w/ employees.
As part of my Results for the Middle-Class #TaxReform Tour, I am traveling the state meeting w/ #Ohio workers who are benefiting from the Tax Cuts & Jobs Act. #Jobs
Today is #HumanTraffickingAwarenessDay. It is a stain on our national character that sex trafficking is increasing. Excited to join survivors & advocates today to push for Senate action on #SESTA.
Pleased to attend signing ceremony for the INTERDICT Act with President Trump at the White House to help give @CustomsBorder agents more tools to help keep fentanyl out. More must be done. #STOPAct
For the 219,000 #Ohio kids, and the 9 million children nationwide who rely on this program, Congress must #SaveCHIP.
It is crucial that countering foreign disinformation & propaganda remain a bipartisan priority. Russian disinfo was a threat long before 2016 and will remain so long after.

Although progress has been made to counter Russian disinformation, much more work remains to be done. Looking forward to working with my Senate Foreign Relations Cmte colleagues to defend our allies, institutions, and values.
Big night for Buckeye basketball! OSU takes down no.1 Michigan State 80-64
.@Nationwide is giving $1,000 bonuses to 29,000 employees and increasing 401(k) matching contributions for 33,000 employees. #TaxReform
.@WesternSouthern is giving $2,000 bonuses to its full-time employees & $1,000 to part-time employees. Goes to all of their more than 3k employees except senior management. #TaxReform
.@FifthThird is raising the base wage to $15 for nearly 3,000 hourly employees & giving $1,000 bonuses to 13,500 employees. #TaxReform
Cincinnati has been feeling the love from @buffalobills fans, so you have my support today... Go Bills!

All over #Ohio, I have met with dedicated people working to help others break the cycle of addiction. I am inspired by their work, & I will continue to do my part at the federal level to help combat the #opiodcrisis. #CARA #STOPAct
Congrats to 2018 #Ohio Teacher of the Year Jonathan Juravich, one of four finalists for Nat'l Teacher of the Year! Proud to have such dedicated educators in OH. #NTOY18
January is National Slavery & Human Trafficking Prevention Month. We must do more to combat this horrific crime & passing #SESTA will help. I urge the Senate to pass it.
After delivering the first significant #taxreform since 1986, I’m optimistic that we will deliver more results this year. It is time for Congress to pass #SESTA, pass the #STOPAct, & more.
I stand in support of Iranians speaking out against oppression and tyranny. Freedom-loving countries around the world should support #IranProtests.
Wishing everyone a Happy New Year! I look forward to getting back to work for #Ohio.
So many great options for fireworks throughout #Ohio for NYE! Where are you and your family headed tonight?
My most important job is representing you, the people of #Ohio. I’m proud of my team’s casework efforts, and I’ll continue to make that, and helping you, a priority.
During my time in the Senate, my office has opened more than 20,000 cases and have saved more than 80% of those successfully. This year alone, we closed almost 3,000 cases favorably.
A highlight of my job is getting to travel the state to meet with #Ohio workers and families from all different backgrounds with all kinds of jobs and interests.
Happy 229th birthday to my hometown of Cincinnati! Proud to call the Queen City home.
Enjoying time in Ohio with Jane and the kids. I hope everyone had a Merry Christmas and is enjoying the holiday season!
.@cavs are on a roll! Hoping to see King James and co get the win against the Warriors today.
Beautiful candlelight service at our church tonight with plenty of carols and a powerful reminder of the meaning of Christmas
Hope every has their holiday shopping done! I’ve still got some to do. Wishing everyone a Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays.
Back home in #Ohio for my favorite time of the year. Family and last minute shopping for gifts. Hope you are getting to spend time with family and loved ones.
Joining @Varneyco on @FoxBusiness to discuss delivering historic #taxreform to the American people. Tune in!

Providing lethal weapons to #Ukraine will send a clear message that America stands with the Ukrainian people in their nearly four year struggle to secure a democratic, prosperous, and independent future for Ukraine in the face of Russian aggression.
The #TaxCutsandJobsAct is now on its way to the president's desk for signature! This is a historic moment, and one that will result in more & better #jobs & higher wages.
#Ohio children rely on CHIP. I'll keep fighting for a long-term re-authorization on behalf of them and their families. #ExtendCHIP
BREAKING: The Senate has passed once-in-a-generation #TaxReform. Passage of these historic tax cuts are a big victory for the American people.
Congratulations to @SpeakerRyan, @RepKevinBrady, @PatTiberi & my colleagues in the House of Representatives for passing #taxreform that will boost the middle class, create #jobs, & raise wages.
Jane & I send our prayers to all those impacted by the train derailment in Washington. Thankful for our first responders at the scene.
.@Cavs vs Wizards never fails to disappoint. Another 57 from the King today?

Hopeful that this week, the president will sign into law legislation that will reform our broken tax code for the first time since 1986. More importantly, it will help deliver long-promised jobs & increased wages.
Happy Wright Brothers Day to all the #Ohio scientists, entrepreneurs, inventors, builders, and doers who carry on their legacy!
#SESTA is supported by victims and advocates, law enforcement, the civil rights community, faith-based groups, and the larger tech community because it will help #EndHumanTrafficking.
The final House-Senate tax agreement preserves important tools for urban renewal that have worked well in Over-the-Rhine in #Cincinnati & other areas of #Ohio, and I fought to preserve them.
Today marks another important milestone in our efforts to provide tax relief for middle-class families and reform our business tax code to create more jobs and increase wages for American workers.
Thanks @SenGillibrand for cosponsoring #SESTA and standing with victims and survivors to help #EndHumanTrafficking.
Had our bipartisan Secret Santa exchange here in the Senate last night. Hope @SenDonnelly from neighboring Indiana gets to enjoy the @GLBC_Cleveland Christmas Ale I got him!
In #Ohio, there are 219,000 kids who get high-quality health coverage through #CHIP. It is critical that Congress #ExtendCHIP to support these children.
Jane and I wish our friends in the Jewish community preparing to celebrate the Festival of Lights a Happy Hanukkah!

I was proud to support bipartisan legislation in the Senate Finance Cmte to extend #CHIP funding so that children & families who rely on this program are not left behind. Full Senate must pass this bill. #ExtendCHIP
Always inspired by our first responders who are so quick to respond and put themselves in danger to protect others. Their response in NYC this morning is another reminder of their heroic efforts.
Seeing a lot of great Christmas decorations around #Ohio this weekend. Nothing beats the Festival of Lights at the @CincinnatiZoo!
We have a once-in-a-generation opportunity to pass a #taxreform bill that will improve our economy and expand opportunity for all Americans. I'll continue to work to get this done.
#SESTA has broad bipartisan support in the Senate because it will help bring traffickers to justice & stop this crime from happening. #EndHumanTrafficking
My hope is that the House and Senate will send a final bill to the president’s desk before Christmas. #TaxReform #Jobs #MiddleClass

In 2010, I made a commitment to the people of #Ohio that I would fight to reform our broken tax code that is driving jobs and investment overseas & to provide relief to families & #smallbiz. This bill does that.
Today, we remember those who were lost in the attack on Pearl Harbor and the incredible sacrifices of the #GreatestGeneration on that day and the years that followed.
#Jerusalem has always been the capital of Israel. I’ve long supported moving the U.S. embassy there, including voting for the bipartisan Jerusalem Embassy Act in 1995.

The last time Congress enacted comprehensive #taxreform, Pete Rose was still playing for the Reds. With the Senate's vote, we are one step closer to deliver much-needed and long-overdue tax relief to the #middleclass.
And the #BigTenChampionship belongs to Ohio State!! Two more games to go.

Last night's vote was an important step forward in reforming our outdated tax code. The Senate #TaxReform plan will cut taxes on the #middleclass, create more & better #jobs, increase wages, and encourage investment here in America.
This is once-in-a-generation #taxreform that will improve our economy and expand opportunity for all Americans. I look forward to working with the House to get this done.

The Tax Cuts & Jobs Act gives families freedom to spend more of their money how they see fit, puts faith in American entrepreneurs & businesses to compete in the global market, & creates a fairer tax system that encourages #jobs and investment in the U.S.

BREAKING: After decades of talk and years of planning, the Senate passed historic reforms that will provide tax relief for #middleclass families, create more #jobs, and increase wages for American workers. #TaxReform
Senate just took another important step toward pro-growth #taxreform that will help the #middleclass, create more #jobs & increase wages. Looking forward to the full debate #VoteARama
This week, the Senate is expected to begin considering the Tax Cuts & Jobs Act on the Senate floor. Looking forward to advancing #taxreform to create more #jobs & increase wages.
Also discussed how #taxreform will help the #middleclass by doubling the standard deduction, doubling the child tax credit & lowering their tax rates #meetthepress #jobs
“The American people deserve to have the highest standards of ethical conduct by their elected leaders” #meetthepress
On @meetthepress, I made clear it’s outrageous that taxpayer funds have been used to fund congressional harassment settlements. This should end.
Looking forward to joining @chucktodd on NBC’s @meetthepress tomorrow to discuss #taxreform, #jobs & more
#Smallbusinesses are the backbone of #Ohio’s economy. #Smallbizsat is an opportunity for all of us to rally behind these businesses that employ so many hard-working Ohioans. #jobs
Tomorrow is #Smallbizsat! Let’s #shopsmall and celebrate the small businesses that are the cornerstone of our #Ohio communities.
So much to be thankful for today! Let's renew our commitment to helping friends & neighbors in need this holiday season. #Thanksgiving
Thinking of our men & women in uniform who can't be home: we all give thanks for their service. #Thanksgiving
From my family to yours, I hope you have a very happy #Thanksgiving!
Looking forward to spending tomorrow with plenty of family and plenty of good food! What are your favorite #Thanksgiving traditions?

Under the Senate #taxreform bill, a median income #Ohio family will save $2,375 annually on their tax bill that they can instead use for gas or groceries, a car payment, retirement, college savings, or a family vacation.

Every week, I hear stories of Ohioans whose lives were cut short due to drug overdoses. Only a few flakes on fentanyl can be lethal - so we must do everything we can to keep these drugs out of our communities. #STOPAct
Congrats to @SpeakerRyan, @RepKevinBrady, @PatTiberi & the House of Representatives for passing meaningful tax relief for the middle class. #TaxReform #Jobs

There are serious issues facing our country: the #opioidcrisis, a tax code that doesn't work for American workers, a scourge of sex trafficking, & threats from #NorthKorea, #Iran, #Russia & others. We must work together to address these issues.

Americans want results, not partisan bickering. In this highly charged political environment, it is more critical than ever that we in Congress find common ground so that we can successfully address the serious issues we face as a country.

Humbled to receive 3 awards this week: the Panetta Institute’s Jefferson-Lincoln Award for Public Policy, the Jacob K. Javits Prize for Bipartisan Leadership, & the Fetal Alcohol Syndrome (NOFAS) Leadership Award. Encourages me to redouble efforts to achieve results.

#TaxReform will do three things. First, it will help address the #middleclass squeeze. Second, it will make American companies more competitive, meaning more & better #jobs & wages. Third, it will level the global playing field and allow us to bring back money from overseas.
For too long, #Ohio workers have had to compete with one arm tied behind their back. The Senate tax plan is good news because it provides a more level playing field for our workers. #Jobs. #TaxReform
It’s crazy that we have a tax code that encourages companies to send #jobs and investment overseas, and it’s outrageous that Congress has allowed this to happen. We need #taxreform now.
Since I came to the Senate in 2011, we've had 70 hearings on #taxreform in the Finance Committee. Looking forward to the open process in committee next week of our new Senate tax reform bill. #Jobs
Happy 242nd birthday to the few, the proud, the United States Marines!  #SemperFi
On this day, I think about my father and grandfather, both of whom were Army infantry officers, and give thanks to them and all our Veterans.
Our veterans made sacrifices to protect the freedoms we enjoy here at home. Jane and I are forever grateful for their service. #VeteransDay

This is a momentous day in our fight to hold online sex traffickers accountable and help give trafficking survivors the justice they deserve. I urge the Senate to act on this bill as quickly as possible. #SESTA #EndHumanTrafficking
BREAKING: #SESTA has unanimously passed the Senate Commerce Committee & is now headed to the Senate floor! #EndHumanTrafficking #CDA230
#SESTA now has 41 bipartisan cosponsors in the Senate. I urge all of my colleagues to support this bill to #EndHumanTrafficking.
Jane & I are devastated by the news out of Sutherland Springs, Texas. We send our prayers to that community & first responders at the scene
Had a blast at The Shoe w/ Jane & friends last weekend. One of the best games I've seen! Hoping our Buckeyes can keep it going in Iowa today
I'm working to put good ideas I've heard into action. #Taxreform is long overdue. Please share your thoughts w me on how to make plan better
Time to deliver results by reducing tax burden on #middleclass, helping American biz grow, & creating better #jobs & wages for our workers.
I commend @realDonaldTrump's opioid commission for putting forward a serious & detailed set of recommendations to help address #opioidcrisis
Jane and I are praying for all those impacted by the terrorist attack in NYC. Thankful for the first responders on the scene immediately.
Fentanyl is now killing more Ohioans than heroin. And it's coming in from overseas. #STOPAct will help keep drugs out & save lives.
Will be on @MeetThePress this morning! Looking forward to discussing #taxreform, #jobs, & more.
4/5 ppl addicted to opioids start out on prescription drugs. Important that we safely dispose of unnecessary prescription meds.#DrugTakeBack
We must act w/ a greater sense of urgency on the part of the admin, this Congress, & key stakeholders to turn the tide of addiction
Appreciated @POTUS' speech today on the #opioidcrisis & his decision to declare it a public health emergency. Positive step forward.
Every day Congress doesn't act, hundreds of American are dying from overdose. We must get the #STOPAct passes ASAP to help save lives.
Voted to provide more resources to Hurricane victims in #PuertoRico, TX & FL & wildfire victims in CA.  Impt we get them the help they need
Big game for the Bengals to get back in the hunt for the AFC North. I’ll be watching  AJ Green! #WhoDey
#TaxReform is urgent. Congress should act ASAP to stop jobs/investment from going overseas & provide working families relief they deserve.
Tune in to @FoxNews at 1pm! Will be discussing #taxreform and how it will create #jobs & boost wages.
.@BenSasse, prediction for the Buckeyes vs Cornhuskers? I'm going with 34-17 good guys. #GoBucks!
We need #taxreform now to help bring more investment to #Ohio. #TaxReform will help create #jobs, boost wages, & bring investment back to US
Washington should do more to help make our #Ohio auto manufacturers more competitive. First & foremost, Congress must pass #TaxReform. #Jobs
At factories in SW, NE, NW & central OH this wk, I was inspired by hard working #Ohio auto workers on the cutting edge of innovation.  #Jobs
The #IranDeal is a deeply-flawed agreement. I look forward to considering legislation to address issues @POTUS
I look forward to taking what I learned on my #Ohio auto tour w/ me back to DC & making a difference for these #Ohio workers. #Jobs
Happy #242NavyBday to our @USNavy Sailors past & present who served to keep our country safe.
Happy #NationalFarmersDay to the thousands of #Ohio farmers who are helping our agriculture industry thrive!
Buckeyes looked great last week against Rutgers. Let's keep the momentum going at The Shoe today! #GoBucks
More & more tech companies are getting on board and supporting #SESTA. Everyone should support this bill to help #EndHumanTrafficking.
#Momentum: Anti-trafficking & faith-based groups, law enforcement, @IBM, @Oracle, @HPE, @21CF, @HomeDepot & @WaltDisneyCo all back #SESTA
Pleased w/ support #SESTA has received from tech companies who support effort to #EndHumanTrafficking. Everyone should support this bill.
Jane & I mourn the loss of innocent lives in this horrific attack in Las Vegas last night.
102 wins & counting! Incredible regular season for the @Indians. Can't wait to see what the post season has in store. #RallyTogether
#SESTA has growing bipartisan support. Please add your voice to those fighting to #endhumantrafficking by encouraging Congress to pass SESTA
#HumanTrafficking is something many think couldn't happen here in America. But it does, & it's happening online at an appalling rate. #SESTA
Pleased to see @POTUS discussing benefits of #taxreform. I'm optimistic we can get this done to provide relief to #Ohio families. #Jobs
Jane and I wish all those observing #YomKippur in Ohio and around the world a meaningful fast. G'mar Chatima Tova
As @POTUS says, this is about creating #jobs and boosting wages. We need to get #TaxReform done for the American people.
Will continue to work w/ @POTUS, @SpeakerRyan, @SenateMajLdr, @OrrinHatch, @RepKevinBrady & others to get #taxreform done & create #jobs
Thx @SenatorBurr for adding your name to the growing list of bipartisan Senators backing the Stop Enabling Sex Traffickers Act (#SESTA).
Thank you @DickDurbin for supporting the bipartisan Stop Enabling Sex Traffickers Act (#SESTA) and your leadership to #EndHumanTrafficking
Important @GOPSenFinance hearing today on the #GrahamCassidy #healthcare plan. Look forward to hearing from the witnesses
Too many #Ohio biz  are saddled w/ burdensome regulations & high taxes. Congress needs to get moving on #taxreform & reg form.
Proud to support conservation efforts in #Ohio and across the country to protect our natural resources for future generations. #NHFday
It is unacceptable that many Chinese companies continue to do business with #NorthKorea, enabling its dangerous and destabilizing actions.
Jane & I are praying for everyone in Puerto Rico and all those in the path of #HurricaneMaria.
At yesterday’s @SenateCommerce hrg, there was bipartisan consensus that Congress must pass #SESTA to help #EndHumanTraficking. #CDA230
Jane & I wish a happy and healthy New Year to all those in #Ohio & around the world observing Rosh Hashana. Shana Tova!
History will judge those who don't help to stop #humantrafficking. This crime is a stain on our national character - and it must stop.#SESTA
I'm fighting to reauthorize #PerkinsLoan Program. It fills an important niche to give low income kids the chance to pursue higher ed
Please join me in celebrating the many contributions of the Hispanic community in #Ohio and around the country. #HHM2017
That is why I am working hard to get #SESTA into law. It will help hold accountable companies like #Backpage that traffic women & children.
Important @SenateCommerce hearing on #SESTA Tuesday to highlight need to help stop online exploitation of women & children. #CDA230
As we provide more resources to address #opioidcrisis, Ohioans will have better access to long-term treatment & recovery programs that work.
Proud to have the support of 21st Century Fox (@21CF) for our bipartisan Stop Enabling Sex Traffickers Act. Support continues to grow.#SESTA
Jane & I are saddened to learn of the passing of former Sen. Pete Domenici. Our thoughts & prayers are with his family.
Proud to chair the Senate #Ukraine Caucus w/ @SenatorDurbin. We will continue to advocate for our Ukrainian friends here in the U.S. Senate
Today marks the 25th anniversary of the United States' diplomatic relations with #Ukraine. Important that the US continue to stand w/ them.

Inspired by the bravery and courage of so many working to save lives down in Texas & Louisiana including #Ohio Task Force One (#OHTF1)

I'll continue to fight for these to create #jobs & boost wages. #Ohio

Wishing hardworking Ohioans a relaxing #LaborDay weekend w/ friends & fam. Hard work fuels US & workers deserve pro-#jobs, pro-work policies

Look forward to hearing more from Sec. Tillerson & Sec. Mattis on how #POTUS’ #Afghanistan strategy will help make America safer.
We cannot allow al Qaeda & our terrorist enemies to again use #Afghanistan as a safe haven from which to launch attacks on the U.S.
Prayers are with our sailors on the #USSJohnSMcCain today. Thank you to search & rescue crews for your ongoing work.
Important that Congress work on #taxreform & reg reform to help give the economy a shot in the arm, boost wages, and create good #jobs.
Jane & I are praying for the victims of the evil terror attack in #Barcelona, and we thank the first responders for their courageous work.
The response to this ideology of hate & bigotry, & the act of domestic terrorism, should be simple & united condemnation without ambiguity.
We must speak out clearly against the hatred, racism and white supremacists who descended upon #Charlottesville.
Exciting announcement: @Facebook is coming to central OH & making a $750M investment! #Ohio continues to grow as a data & tech hub. #Jobs

Praying for the victims & their families from the tragedy in Charlottesville. And I am thankful for our law enforcement across the country.
